咁撚鐘意食栗米，我就叫麥當勞整多啲粟米食死你班仆街</blockquote><br />\n毒撚真係好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 M記粟米再問佢拎牛油 正!<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n整多啲粟米好呀<br />\n求之不得添呀"},{"pid":"4b6af49ee04bd4b3b4917a131029d2f965c2491d","tid":447902,"uid":153277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T02:22:55.000Z","msg":"關你撚事<br />\n我中意食粟米呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a7d20555a06ccf793705bdc675b2c4dc996b0c9","tid":447902,"uid":1749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T02:38:36.000Z","msg":"關你撚事"},{"pid":"964a7951b9dc220f07cfd521c608461b0da85395","tid":447902,"uid":7709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T02:49:09.000Z","msg":"我仲憎鳩你添啦，屌你老母<br />\n你唔撚去死？"},{"pid":"523a6fba075e2d905f35a7fafdfbf808ee4f6082","tid":447902,"uid":16343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T02:50:38.000Z","msg":"D毒撚連人地食咩都要理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18dbfcf7fd86c61e4607537e066588c344b89b12","tid":447902,"uid":83094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T02:52:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"52067773e3f3d34999c37744be92b121ea466d70","tid":447902,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T02:53:33.000Z","msg":"樓豬做m記？"},{"pid":"cabc6d2643d24c4f98385a4d5558be5a0d1a5538","tid":447902,"uid":64961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T02:56:10.000Z","msg":"依家唔洗加錢有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾年前要加4蚊轉就不了"},{"pid":"fb7f2a27c6f6f4b4f514ed99e5258c5bdb2e0457","tid":447902,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T03:10:07.000Z","msg":"我係鍾意食粟米咁又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class